---
title: Thai Coconut Curry Noodles with Veggies & Roasted Peanuts
description: Set your timers: this fragrant dish comes together in 25 minutes or less, yet has the flavour of a slow-cooked meal. With crisp and tender vegetables and crunchy peanuts all coated in a luscious coconut curry sauce, this bowl of Thai noodles is a fast food choice you can feel happy about!
